    public static class AuthProfile.CritObjectAnalyze
extends org.apache.beam.sdk.transforms.DoFn<Event,Alert>

    Analysis for authentication involving critical objects

    Analyze events to determine if they are related to any objects configured as being critical objects. Where identified, generate critical level alerts.
